flowchart TD
    Start([Start replay of Project A]) --> Load[Load ordered Step rows]
    Load --> Next{Next step?}
    Next -- no --> Done([Chain complete])
    Next -- yes --> Disabled{IsDisabled = 1?}
    Disabled -- yes --> Next
    Disabled -- no --> Attempt[Attempt step<br/>bounded by TimeoutMs]
    Attempt --> Outcome{Success?}
    Outcome -- yes --> SuccessLink{OnSuccessProjectId set?}
    SuccessLink -- yes --> Enqueue[Enqueue replayProject<br/>depth cap = 1]
    SuccessLink -- no --> Next
    Enqueue --> Next
    Outcome -- no --> Retry{Retries left?}
    Retry -- yes --> Attempt
    Retry -- no --> Report[Emit FailureReport<br/>Phase 03 error-manage]
    Report --> FailureLink{OnFailureProjectId set?}
    FailureLink -- yes --> Dispatch[replayProject failure branch]
    FailureLink -- no --> Halt([Halt chain])
    Dispatch --> Halt
